reviewText: I would like to have a copy of this to put in Street collection

I am Jason Korsiak, the writer and director of Freddy's Return. Our film, released November 16, 2009, is a fan film made for fans, not profit. Without buying it, which I refuse to, I cannot attest to the quality, but it is not the complete film, which is readily available to view on YouTube for free. Please, no not support this seller or this product.
